
OpenCV installatiion: 

Refer to this Link: https://www.pyimagesearch.com/2017/09/04/raspbian-stretch-install-opencv-3-python-on-your-raspberry-pi/
                    and follow each steps carefully.
                    
                    installation takes about 5 hours.
                    
                    
Espeak installation: open terminal of raspbian and type : sudo apt-get install espeak

GPIO library installation :  open terminal of raspbian and type : sudo apt-get install rpi.gpio 
                    
                    
